
==============================================
         UMKM Insight Server v3.0
         Sistem Analitik Read-Only + SaaS
==============================================
  Backend  : http://localhost:8080
  Database : MySQL (XAMPP)
  Mode     : READ-ONLY (transaksi keuangan)
  Source   : SmartBank (Dummy Data)
  Lang     : Python + Flask Framework
==============================================
  API Endpoints:
  POST /api/auth/register
  POST /api/auth/login
  GET  /api/auth/me
  GET  /api/umkm_insight/dashboard
  GET  /api/umkm_insight/ambil_data_transaksi
  GET  /api/umkm_insight/analisis_penjualan
  GET  /api/umkm_insight/biaya_akses_analytics
  GET  /api/smartbank/pay
  GET  /api/admin/users
  GET  /api/admin/stats
==============================================

 * Serving Flask app 'app.server'
 * Debug mode: off
